# Optional: override WebRTC signaling server URL (default: same host as page, port 8080).
# See docs/SIGNAL_SERVER.md for details.
# Same machine (Docker): use wss://localhost:8080 — do not use the container IP (e.g. 172.19.0.2).
# From phone: leave unset and open app at https://<your-PC-LAN-IP>:5173 so signaling uses wss://<LAN-IP>:8080.
# VITE_SIGNALING_URL=wss://localhost:8080
